# _headers — CLASS 3 REFERENCE TEMPLATE (goes in your llm/ folder)
#
# Cloudflare Pages applies these security headers to every page of the bot
# surface. Pages's build-output directory is set to llm/, so it only ever sees
# what's in that folder. Copy this file to llm/_headers as-is — it's safe,
# generic, and needs no per-site changes.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
